    ('REL-A 270', 'INTRODUCTION TO ISLAM', '13306', 'Class Status', 'MW Monday, Wednesday 3:35 PM–5:10 PM', 'SW 007', 'Robert Jaques', 67, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'SWAIN WEST', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Introduction to the religious world of Islam: the Arabian milieu before Muhammad''s prophetic call, the career of the Prophet. Qur''an and hadith, ritual and the pilars of Muslim praxis, legal, and theological traditions; mysticism and devotional piety, reform and revivalist movements.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd A&H credit
